title: Bobby Brings In Future Country Stars From TikTok + Amy Presents Her Marriage Court Case + The Morning Corny...After Dark!
itunes:title: Bobby Brings In Future Country Stars From TikTok + Amy Presents Her Marriage Court Case + The Morning Corny...After Dark!
description:
Bobby brings in each of the four finalists from his search for new country artists on TikTok. Sean Williams, Brittany Moore, Taylor Acorn and Gray Robinson all come in to perform one of their songs and a cover! Amy brings us her situation that she had with her husband involving a towel. Per listener request…Amy delivers her “Morning Corny After Dark”. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
